== 市場反應 ==
[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]給予憤怒的小鳥里約大冒險版本88分（滿分100分）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/angry-birds-rio |title=Angry Birds Rio for iPhone/iPad Reviews |publisher=Metacritic |date= |accessdate=2014-01-02 |archive-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727080156/https://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/angry-birds-rio |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但有[[Pocket_Gamer|Pocket Gamer]]用戶指出遊戲雖然質素高，但欠缺新意<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPhone/Angry+Birds+Rio/review.asp?c=28581|title=Angry Birds Rio Review|author=Tracy Erickson|work=PocketGamer.co.uk|date=2011-03-23|accessdate=2012-12-17|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915171831/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPhone/Angry+Birds+Rio/review.asp?c=28581|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{NoteTag|1=原文：「what Angry Birds Rio lacks in new ideas and freshness, it makes up in quality gameplay and good value」}}；遊戲評價網站[[Gamezebo|Gamezebo]]也有用戶指出遊戲「有點反高潮」<ref name="Gamezebo" />{{NoteTag|1=原文：「a little anti-climactic」}}。

自從推出，憤怒的小鳥里約大冒險版本已被下載超過一千萬次<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2383049,00.asp|title=Angry Birds Rio Downloaded 10M Times|author=Chloe Albanesius|work=PCMag.com|date=2011-04-04|accessdate=2011-04-20|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915171834/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2383049,00.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於[[Apple_App_Store|Apple App Store]]及[[Google_Play|Google Play]]成為最熱門的應用程式之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36820/Top_iPad_Game_Apps_Contre_Jour_Peggle_HD_See_FastSelling_Debuts.php |title=News - Top iPad Game Apps: Contre Jour, Peggle HD See Fast-Selling Debuts |publisher=Gamasutra |date= |accessdate=2012-04-25 |archive-date=2018-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915171835/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36820/Top_iPad_Game_Apps_Contre_Jour_Peggle_HD_See_FastSelling_Debuts.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36583/Top_iPhone_Game_Apps_Cover_Orange_Leads_Free_Charts.php |title=News - Top iPhone Game Apps: Cover Orange Leads Free Charts |publisher=Gamasutra |date= |accessdate=2012-04-25 |archive-date=2018-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915171835/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36583/Top_iPhone_Game_Apps_Cover_Orange_Leads_Free_Charts.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36835/Top_Android_Game_Apps_Cut_the_Rope_Death_Worm_Head_Platform_Sales.php |title=News - Top Android Game Apps: Cut the Rope, Death Worm Head Platform Sales |publisher=Gamasutra |date= |accessdate=2012-04-25 |archive-date=2018-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915171838/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36835/Top_Android_Game_Apps_Cut_the_Rope_Death_Worm_Head_Platform_Sales.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.androidrank.org/details?id=com.rovio.angrybirdsrio |title=Angry Birds Rio |publisher=Androidrank |date= |accessdate=2012-04-25 |archiv